name: 透
text: 寝てないみたいな顔だね
trans: Looks like you haven't gotten any sleep.

name: 透
trans: Were you watching videos or something?

text:
動画なら
いいんだけどな
trans:
Would've been nice
if it was videos.

name: 透
text: 忙しいアピールってやつなの？

name: 透
text:
なんか深刻だね……
頑張って
trans:
This suddenly went kind of deep...
Do your best.

name: 透
text:
ちょっと
冗談言っただけ
trans: I was just making a little joke.

name: プロデューサー
text: （うっ……しまった。別のことを言えば良かったな……）
trans: (Ah... I should've said something else instead...)
